伊朗又一官员确诊去世，当地开建“火神山”。
Another Iranian official was confirmed dead and a mountain of fire was built there.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 喻晓璇海外网海外网3月3日消息，据Al Arabiya新闻网报道，伊朗国家电视台援引国会副议长的消息称，目前已经有23名国会议员被确诊感染新冠病毒。
Iranian state television quoted a deputy speaker of parliament as saying that 23 members of parliament have been diagnosed with the new crown virus, the newspaper Al Arabiya News reported.
另据阿拉伯国有电视台(Al Arabiya)报道，伊朗紧急卫生服务部负责人Pir Hossein Kolivand感染新冠病毒。
Also according to Al Arabiya, the head of Iran's emergency health service, Pir Hossein Kolivand, was infected with the new crown virus.
伊朗媒体报道说，该国司法部长的一名顾问因新冠病毒感染去世。
Iranian media reports say an adviser to the country's justice minister has died of a New Crown virus.
据伊朗卫生部最新消息，3月3日伊朗累计确诊新冠肺炎病例2336例，其中77例死亡，死亡率约3.29%。
According to the latest news from the Iranian Ministry of Health, the cumulative number of confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in Iran on March 3 was 2,336, including 77 deaths and a mortality rate of about 3.29 per cent.
随着确诊病例不断增加，伊朗的防疫工作也正在如火如荼地推进。
With the number of confirmed cases increasing, immunization efforts in Iran are proceeding apace.
近日，伊朗多个城市开建专用于收治新冠病毒感染者的传染病医院。
In recent days, several cities in Iran have opened hospitals dedicated to treating people infected with the new crown virus.
在伊朗中部城市亚兹德，政府承诺将在数日内建成一所占地1000平方米的医院。
In the central Iranian city of Yazd, the government has pledged to build a 1,000-square-metre hospital within days.
在疫情最先爆发的圣城库姆，伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队也建起了一所野战医院专门收治新冠肺炎病人。
In the holy city of Qom, the epicentre of the outbreak, Iran's Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps also built a field hospital to treat patients with pneumonia.
从首次宣布有确诊病例以来，伊朗已经在不到两周时间内成为中国境外确诊病例数第二多的国家，仅次于韩国。
Since the first confirmed case was announced, Iran has become the country with the second highest number of confirmed cases outside China in less than two weeks, after South Korea.
建设中的野战医院伊朗版“火神山”开建据伊朗塔斯尼姆通讯社3月2日报道，伊朗中部城市亚兹德正集中力量建成一家专门用于收治新冠病毒感染者的医院。
Iran's central city of Yazd is concentrating its efforts to build a hospital dedicated to treating people infected with the virus, the news agency said Wednesday.
亚兹德市基础设施和运输部副部长马哈茂德·德甘（Mahmoud Dehghan）表示，该医院的建设已经从3月1日开始进行，如果一切按照计划实施，将于本周晚些时候完工，随后将交付医疗设备开始正式运营。
Mahmoud Dehghan, deputy minister of infrastructure and transport in Yazd city, said construction of the hospital had begun on March 1 and, if everything went according to plan, would be completed later this week and medical equipment would be delivered for full operation.
塔斯尼姆通讯社报道称，上述医院占地1000平方米，设有急诊病房、医护人员休息区和生物医疗废物集中区。
The hospital covers an area of 1,000 square meters and has emergency wards, a medical staff rest area and a biomedical waste collection area, Tusnim reported.
俄罗斯卫星通讯社认为，这所医院的建设让人联想到中国武汉上个月在短短一周时间内建成的“火神山”和“雷神山”医院。
The building of the hospital is reminiscent of the "mountain of fire" and "mountain of thunder" hospitals built by Wuhan in China last month, according to the Russian satellite news agency.
革命卫队地面部队进入警戒状态在疫情最严重的圣城库姆，伊斯兰革命卫队也新建了一所专门收治新冠病毒感染者的野战医院。
Revolutionary Guard Corps ground troops on alert in the worst of the epidemic in the holy city of Qom, Islamic Revolutionary Guards Corps also set up a dedicated New Crown virus treatment field hospital.
据伊朗半官方媒体Iran Press报道，该野战医院位于库姆的工业区，设有180张床位，由急诊室、高级诊室、放射科、住院部和药房组成。
According to Iran Press, an Iranian parastatal media, the field hospital is located in the industrial area of Qom and has 180 beds and consists of emergency rooms, advanced rooms, radiology departments, inpatient departments and pharmacies.
野战医院的医生另据塔斯尼姆通讯社报道，伊斯兰革命卫队地面部队指挥官穆罕默德·帕克普尔表示，为了对抗新冠肺炎疫情，他所在的部队已经建立起了一个“生物行动基地”，伊斯兰革命卫队的生物学和病毒学专家也已经部署到了伊朗受病毒影响较大的地区。
Doctors at the field hospital also reported that the IRGC ground force commander Muhammad Pakpur had set up a "biological base of operations" to combat the outbreak, and that IRGC biology and virology experts had been deployed to areas of the country most affected by the virus, Tusnim reported.
帕克普尔还补充说，伊斯兰革命卫队地面卫队十个基地的所有现代化装备军事单位均已处于警戒状态。
He added that all modern military units at 10 IRGC ground guard bases were on alert.
与此同时，伊斯兰革命卫队的医疗队已经准备好了定点医院、流动医院及快速反应医疗队，协助伊朗卫生部开展工作。
At the same time, IRGC medical teams have been prepared to locate hospitals, mobile hospitals and rapid reaction teams to assist the Iranian Ministry of Health.
军队停止招募新兵此外，伊朗还开始重视军队防疫工作。
The army has stopped recruiting new recruits, and Iran has begun to pay attention to army immunization.
伊朗武装力量已经推迟了原定于未来几周进行的义务兵役招募活动。
The Iranian armed forces have postponed compulsory military service recruitment, which was scheduled to take place in the coming weeks.
据有美国背景的伊朗新闻网站Radio Farda报道，伊朗武装力量新冠病毒战斗工作组发言人哈桑·阿拉基扎准将3月2日宣布，决定将新兵入伍工作推迟至少两个月。
According to the United States-backed Iranian news website Radio Farda, Brigadier General Hassan Alakiza, spokesman for the Armed Forces New Crown Virus Combat Working Group, announced on 2 March that it had decided to postpone the recruitment process for at least two months.
伊朗正规军地面部队医疗部门负责人贝赫扎德·莫阿泽尼准将3月1日在接受伊朗劳工通讯社（ILNA）采访时表示，军队正采取一切适当措施，防止冠状病毒在军中扩散。
In an interview with the Iranian Labor News Agency (ILNA) on March 1, Brigadier General Behzad Moazeni, head of the ground unit of the Iranian regular army, said the army was taking all appropriate measures to prevent the coronavirus from spreading in the army.
莫阿泽尼表示，军队的培训课程及集体祈祷活动已被取消。
Moazeni said army training courses and group prayers had been cancelled.
据莫阿泽尼所说，截至目前，伊朗陆军部队中尚未发现新冠病毒感染病例。
So far, according to Moazeni, no new cases of crown virus infection have been detected in Iranian army units.
